    <item>
      <title>维旺迪旗下 Canal+ 增持毛里求斯付费电视公司股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/vivendi-s-canal-increases-stake-in-mauritian-pay-tv-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国公司 Vivendi SE 旗下的 Canal+ 计划将其在 MC Vision 的股份增加一倍，成为这家位于毛里求斯的数字付费电视公司的大股东，以扩大其在非洲大陆的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/vivendi-s-canal-increases-stake-in-mauritian-pay-tv-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德拉希退出英国电信前，其所持股份价值缩水 13 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/drahi-s-bt-exit-follows-1-3-billion-drop-in-stake-s-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社计算，帕特里克·德拉希 (Patrick Drahi) 正在撤出其在英国电信公司 BT Group Plc 的投资，此前其所持股份的价值已缩水约 9.909 亿英镑（12.6 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/drahi-s-bt-exit-follows-1-3-billion-drop-in-stake-s-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克央行宣布谨慎降息 通胀加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/czech-inflation-quickens-as-central-bank-flags-cautious-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克 7 月份通胀意外加速，进一步表明央行在进一步放松货币政策方面需谨慎。克朗上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/czech-inflation-quickens-as-central-bank-flags-cautious-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 07:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gold Fields 以 16 亿美元收购加拿大 Osisko</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/gold-fields-buys-canada-s-osisko-in-1-6-billion-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于贵金属价格飙升，促使生产商寻求扩张，Gold Fields Ltd. 同意以 21.6 亿加元（16 亿美元）的价格收购加拿大 Osisko Mining Inc.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/gold-fields-buys-canada-s-osisko-in-1-6-billion-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:47:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨索尔美国业务受创 减记 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/sasol-to-report-full-year-loss-on-3-billion-of-impairments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨索尔有限公司将主要针对其美国业务减记 551 亿兰特（30 亿美元），该业务的扩张增加了其面临的一系列挑战，包括化学品价格下跌和降低碳排放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/sasol-to-report-full-year-loss-on-3-billion-of-impairments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:24:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
